{
  "texts": [
    "The collected database was composed by 1259 answers to the questionnaire.",
    "Among them, 42 were discarded for several reasons, as incompleteness, impossibility of verifying the presence of dyslexia, comorbidities with other SLDs, non-compliance with the four criteria exposed in the \"Data collection\" section and random filling.",
    "The participants that fall into the last categories were detected by the expert psychologists.",
    "However, in order not to perturbate the results, they discarded only the very evident cases of random filling as, for example, questionnaires in which the same answer was given to more than 80% of the items, or a questionnaire in which the participant stated that they did not know any of the support tools.",
    "The remaining 1217 answers were preprocessed, in order to have a suitable data format to run ML algorithms training and testing."
  ]
}